INSERT INTO `zt_tp_product` VALUES ('avQd5ZCTxjxF', '', '1', '9h0zez', 'fKAKiC', '1', '1', 'iMac', '<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iMac是一款苹果电脑，针对消费者和教育市场的一体化苹果<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Macintosh\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Macintosh</a>电脑系列。 iMac的特点是它的设计， 由于iMac在设计上的独特之处和出众的易用性，它几乎连年获奖。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2017年6月5日至9日，在苹果开发者大会2017上，发布了iMac Pro。这是苹果史上性能最强的iMac，它搭载了最多18核至强处理器，整体的浮点运算能力达到惊人的22Teraflops（每秒22万亿浮点运算）。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background-image: url(&quot;https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png&quot;); background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; position: relative; text-indent: 0px;\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">发展历史</h2><a class=\"edit-icon j-edit-link\" data-edit-dl=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); display: block; float: right; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; padding-left: 24px; font-size: 12px; font-family: SimSun; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma\" style=\"font-family: baikeFont_layout; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; speak: none; line-height: 1; outline: 0px; margin: 0px 3px 0px 0px; vertical-align: text-bottom; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"></span>编辑</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">iMac G3</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iMac/1017925/0/3bf33a87e950352ae4802db15343fbf2b3118ba1?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"1998年的imac\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 165px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=d5dfac06a0ec08fa220014a569ef3d4d/3bf33a87e950352ae4802db15343fbf2b3118ba1.jpg\" alt=\"1998年的imac\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 165px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">1998年的imac</span></div></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">(\"果冻式 iMac\")</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">1998年8月15日，— —iMac配置233 MHz处理器。具有2 MB图形处理。只有邦迪蓝配色。1998年10月17日，— —iMac更新成MacOS 8.5，ATI 图形处理与6兆字节的SDRAM。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">1999年1月5日，— —iMac升级266 MHz处理器。把IrDA端口和夹层插槽删除。6 MB 图形处理。新增草莓红、 邦迪蓝、 青柠绿、葡萄紫 和越橘配色。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">1999年4月14日，— —iMac升级333 MHz处理器。更新了鼠标按钮。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">1999年10月5日— —iMac/iMac DV/iMac DVSE。第一代、 支持FireWire。可选350或400 MHz处理器，新增CD托盘式光碟机，特别版颜色与石墨颜色相同。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2000年7月19日— —iMac/iMac DV/iMac DV +DVSE。 可选350、400、450或500 MHz的处理器。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2001年2月22日— — iMac，可选400、500 或600、MHz处理器。在靛蓝，石墨，蓝色或红色颜色中可用。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2001年7月18日— — iMac， 可选500、600 或700、MHz 处理器。在靛蓝、 石墨、 和白色颜色中可用<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[2]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[2]_56081\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a>&nbsp;。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">iMac G4</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">（\"台灯式 iMac<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">\")</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">iMac G4 2002年1月7日 – 苹果电脑推出新的 iMac 产品线，共有三种形式。他们具有未来感的外表因素，包含 700 或 800 MHz 的 G4 处理器，而且只有白色。显示器是 15 寸 LCD，使用一个可摆动的器臂来定位。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 169px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iMac/1017925/0/d50735fae6cd7b893f8f4c3b0f2442a7d8330ea2?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2002年的imac\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 169px; height: 220px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=090dbe974134970a4373172da5cbd1c0/d50735fae6cd7b893f8f4c3b0f2442a7d8330ea2.jpg\" alt=\"2002年的imac\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 169px; height: 220px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">2002年的imac</span></div>2002年7月17日 – 新的型号推出，拥有 17 寸 LCD 和 800 MHz 或是 1 GHz 的处理器，更大的硬盘空间（最大到 80 GB) 和更新的 绘图芯片。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2003年2月4日 – 产品线减为两种型号，一种是 15 寸 LCD，另一种是 17 寸 LCD。AirPort Extreme 也和蓝牙，和 DDR 内存（第一次在 iMac 的历史出现） 都含在 17 寸的型号。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2003年8月 – iMac 15 和 17 寸的型号分别升级到 1 GHz 和 1.25 GHz G4 处理器。两者都支援 USB 2.0，AirPort Extreme，蓝牙，以及 DDR 内存。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2003年11月18日 – 20 寸的屏幕型号推出，可以显示 1680*1050 的屏幕分辨率，以及 1.25 GHz 的 G4 处理器。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">iMac G5</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iMac/1017925/0/0e2442a7d933c89576adeec3d11373f0830200b2?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2004年的imac\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 209px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=32249240a786c9170c03553bf93c70c6/0e2442a7d933c89576adeec3d11373f0830200b2.jpg\" alt=\"2004年的imac\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 209px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">2004年的imac</span></div>2004年8月31日 –&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">苹果电脑</a>推出全新的 iMac 产品线，拥有 LCD 荧幕 （17或20寸宽荧幕）和电脑（包含电源供应）本身，包含在一个 2 寸厚的平面显示器上，使用 1.6 或 1.8 GHz PowerPC G5 64位元 处理器，特色为一个 Serial ATA 硬盘 （在教育版型号是Parallel ATA) 和 Nvidia GeForce 5200 绘图处理晶片。USB 2、FireWire 400、和 10/100Base-T 以太网接口、V.92 数据机、视频输出接口、类比语音输入孔、和结合类比/mini-TOSLINK的语音输出孔 （类似在 AirPort Express 的单元） 和独立摆置在后方的电源按钮。整个外观是由一个铝制的悬臂撑在桌面上，也可以使用 VESA 挂载平板来取代，让整个机身可以用任何 VESA 标准的挂载点来悬挂。<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">苹果电脑</a>声称这是市场上最薄的桌上型电脑。iMac G5 有三种零售型号，加上一种只供教育用没有光碟机的型号，没有数据机，和最简单的 GeForce MX4000 绘图显示系统。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2005年3月3日，– 苹果电脑 极大地更新 iMac 产品线，把主板上的内存加到 512MB。入门型号为1.8 GHz，最高型号达到 2 GHz。可选购的升级配备现在包含双层 8x SuperDrive。所有的型号现在都含有 AirPort Extreme 无线网路，蓝牙 2.0，和 ATI Technologies Radeon 9600 显示晶片及 标准 128MB 的视讯记忆体空间。所有的型号现在都与 iLife \'05 和最新的 Mac OS X 10.4 \"Tiger\" 一起搭配出售。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">iMac Core Duo</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iMac/1017925/0/64380cd7912397dd89b4eebc5982b2b7d1a287bc?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2007年的imac\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 147px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=67ba632c462309f7e36faa10420f0c39/64380cd7912397dd89b4eebc5982b2b7d1a287bc.jpg\" alt=\"2007年的imac\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 147px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">2007年的imac</span></div>2006年1月10日 – 苹果电脑推出使用Intel处理器的iMac，速度加快了2至3倍。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">17\" 机型 (MA199LL),1.83 GHz Intel Core Duo</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">20\" 机型 (MA200LL),2.0 GHz Intel Core Duo</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">一个PCI-Express架构下、128MB DDR VRAM的ATI Radeon X1600显示晶片，2.0 GHz机型搭载256 MB DDR VRAM。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2006 年夏天，苹果又推出 24 英寸的 iMac，同时对现有的 iMac 进行降价。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">同年推出的Boot Camp更是让iMac可以使用Windows操作系统。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">iMac Core 2 Duo</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2009年10月20日苹果公司推出全新的iMac，配备炫丽的21.5和27英寸的LED背光宽显示屏，并拥有全新无框玻璃设计和无缝的全铝机身，配备3.06GHz以上的Intel Core 2 Duo处理器，以及Core i5四核处理器。　苹果最近将 iMac 由过去的 Core Duo 处理器升级到更快的 Core 2 Duo 处理器，处理器有2.4GHz,2.66GHz,2.8GHz，和3.06GHz可供选择。同时新增加了24’特大版本，这款iMac电脑第一次采用了nⅥDIA的7300GT显示卡，随着ATi被收购，此举也意味着Apple和Nvidia走的越来越近。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">由于 Intel 处理器的介入，iMac 可以像其他的 PC 一样安装 Windows 系统。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">iMac Core i</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2010 年7月27号，苹果推出装有Core i3\\i5\\i7的iMac，有i3 540 3.06 Dual Core\\i3 550 3.2 Dual Core\\i5 760 Quad 2.8\\i7 870 Quad 2.93，型号为分别MC508\\MC509\\MC510\\MC511</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">它们装配ATI RADEON HD4670 GD3 256M \\ HD5670 GD5 512M \\ HD5750 GD5 1G三款显示卡。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">显示器尺寸为21.5寸（1920-1080）和27寸（2560-1440）</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">这代机型中，Apple摒弃了英伟达（NVIDIA）显卡</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">iMac Sandy Bridge</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iMac/1017925/0/4bed2e738bd4b31c4917e50387d6277f9e2ff85b?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"imac sandy bridge\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 203px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=593d908f35fae6cd08b4ac633fb20f9e/4bed2e738bd4b31c4917e50387d6277f9e2ff85b.jpg\" alt=\"imac sandy bridge\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 203px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">imac sandy bridge</span></div>美国当地时间5月3日周二上午，苹果终于发布了其台式一体机iMac系列更新。新款iMac保留了时尚的铝制和玻璃外观，搭载四核Intel Core i5和i7处理器、全新AMD图形处理器、Thunderbolt传输技术以及FaceTime HD高清摄像头。与前代相比，新款iMac内核速度提升了1.7倍，图形处理速度则提升了足足3倍之多。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">新款iMac仍只提供两种屏幕尺寸，21.5英寸和27英寸，9298元起售。每个尺寸分为两种机型，分别是主频2.5GHz和2.7GHz，以及主频 2.7GHz和3.1GHz，标准配置均为四核Intel Core i5处理器，但2.7GHz的21.5寸机型可以定制2.8GHz四核Intel Core i7处理器， 3.1GHz的27寸机型可以定制 3.4GHz 四核 Intel Core i7 处理器。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">硬盘方面，除了9298元低配的机型只有500GB外，其他三款机型均配备1TB的硬盘，并且还可升级到2TB或附加 256GB 固态硬盘。四款机型的内存均为4GB （两个 2GB) 的 1333MHz DDR3 内存，在苹果在线商店预订的顾客还可定制 16GB 内存。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">苹果<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iMac/1017925/0/503d269759ee3d6dc6f2132243166d224f4ade27?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2012 版iMac\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 165px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=198b18d84a90f60300b09b450913b370/503d269759ee3d6dc6f2132243166d224f4ade27.jpg\" alt=\"2012 版iMac\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 165px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">2012 版iMac</span></div>在此次更新的iMac采用的图形处理器足以强大，全系列配备先进的 AMD Radeon HD 高清独立图形处理器，甚至最高配置的27寸机型还能定制具备 2GB GDDR5 显存的 AMD Radeon HD 6970M 图形处理器，是<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">高端玩家</a>的理想配置。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">内置的FaceTime HD高清摄像头支持高清晰画质的视频聊天，可与任何安装有FaceTime的Mac、iPad 2、iPhone 4和第四代iPod touch拨打高清<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%94%B5%E8%AF%9D\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">视频电话</a>。全新宽屏格式看得更清更广。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">苹果在21.5 英寸 iMac 配备一个 Thunderbolt 端口，而在27 英寸 iMac 配备两个 Thunderbolt 端口，其他端口配置与前代一样。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">除了苹果无线键盘，顾客还可在Magic Mouse和Magic Trackpad之间任选一款，打造属于自己的台式电脑。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">iMac Ivy Bridge</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">时间：北京时间10月24日凌晨1点。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">地点：美国圣何塞加州剧院。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">新款iMac包含21.5英寸和27英寸两款机型，分辨率分别为1920×1080和2560×1440，21.5英寸版并未搭载众人期待的retina视网膜屏，但是经过重新设计的屏幕，将外层玻璃与显示屏之间的保护膜去掉，将外层玻璃紧贴显示屏，这样可有效减少75%的反光，并使画面更加动人。搭载Core i7处理器，最高3TB存储器(Fusion Drive)，你可以选择 128GB 的SSD，然后再选用1TB或者3TB的传统硬盘。以及768GB的全SSD。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">机身设计上，新款iMac最薄处相比上一代机型薄了80%，可视角度可达178度。接口方面，新品内置SDXC卡插槽、4个USB3.0、2个Thunderbolt以及Mini Display等接口。27吋机型同样未配备Retina视网膜显示屏，21.5英寸版最早将于11月开始发售，27英寸版将于12月发售。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">新iMac采用新的Friction Stir Welding制造工艺，让其机身最薄处达到了5mm，是目前全球最薄的一体机电脑，成为新款很耀眼的一大亮点。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 196px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iMac/1017925/0/4ec2d5628535e5dd12a2033a76c6a7efcf1b624d?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2012 iMac\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 196px; height: 220px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=ae065a3f15ce36d3a60484320af23a24/4ec2d5628535e5dd12a2033a76c6a7efcf1b624d.jpg\" alt=\"2012 iMac\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 196px; height: 220px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">2012 iMac</span></div>其中21.5寸的虽然没有采用Retina视网膜屏，但是对于1920X1080的分辨率来说，搭载的NVIDIA GT 640M对于运行一些大型3D游戏的用户来说还是有点吃力。而27英寸的最低搭载GTX 660M显卡，对于游戏用户来说可能会是一个不错的选择。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">最新iMac已经于11月3日全球同步开售，其中包括中国大陆地区以及香港地区，此次开售的产品共两款，两款均为21.5英寸产品，标准配置的价格分别是9688和10988元。而27英寸新款iMac已经于1月面向中国地区开售。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">iMac with Retina Display</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2014年10月17日，备受关注的苹果秋季发布会上，期待已久的重磅新品——27英寸的iMac震撼亮相，带来了多方面的升级，最让我们震惊的，当属其高达5K的超清晰屏幕，分辨率达到5120 x 2880，无疑这是一个奇迹。新的iMac搭配了视网膜屏幕，可以显示高清图像，5K的显示屏比传统4K规格高出了67%，是1080P高清电视的7倍，拥有1470万像素。这样的升级无与伦比，而这样27英寸的高清屏幕，边缘处只有仅仅5mm厚度。也是目前该系列中最好的产品。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[4]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[4]_56081\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">硬件方面，起售配置采用第四代i5处理器，主频为3.5GHz（也可以选择4GHz i7），图形方面选择了AMD的Radeon R9，内存8GB，Thunderbolt 2接口以及1TB fusion硬盘。其实外观方面和上一代产品并没有很大改变。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[5]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[5]_56081\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2015年10月15日消息，全新21.5英寸4K iMac和27英寸5K iMac已经在本周早些时候上架。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[6]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[6]_56081\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">新款21.5英寸4KiMac 运行的是3.1GHz四核<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Intel\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Intel</a>Core<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/i5\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">i5</a>处理器，高端21.5英寸iMac（无Retina屏幕）配备的是2.8GHz四核Intel Core i5处理器，新款27英寸5K iMac有运行3.2GHz四核Intel Core i5处理器的低端版本，运行3.3GHz处理器的相对较高端的27英寸iMac 。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">在这次更新的iMac中，除了首次为21.5英寸iMac配备了绚丽夺目的全新Retina 4K显示屏之外，所有的27英寸iMac也都配备了Retina 5K显示屏。此次更新的iMac还配备更加强劲的中央处理器和图形处理器、两个Thunderbolt 2端口和全新存储方案选择，以及高性能Fusion Drive。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">另外苹果还针对新款iMac推出了新的配件产品，包括Magic Keyboard全尺寸键盘、Magic Mouse 2鼠标、以及整合了Force Touch的Magic Trackpad 2。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">当地时间2017年6月5日至9日，苹果开发者大会2017（WWDC 2017）<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iMac/1017925/0/838ba61ea8d3fd1fc8f0b7573a4e251f94ca5fe5?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 136px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=bf150f73b3389b503cffe750b534e5f1/838ba61ea8d3fd1fc8f0b7573a4e251f94ca5fe5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 136px;\"></a></div>在加州圣何塞的McEnery会议中心举行。在本次WWDC 2017上，发布了硬件产品iMac Pro。这是苹果史上性能最强的iMac，它搭载了最多18核至强处理器，同时这款性能强大的iMac Pro还采用了AMD最新的Vega显卡。整体的浮点运算能力达到惊人的22Teraflops（每秒22万亿浮点运算），内置5K Retina屏幕，雷电3接口，最大搭载128GB ECC高速缓存，全面支持VR、4K视频，用户甚至可以用来做深度学习项目的开发。</div></div>', '', '颜色', '尺寸', 'CPU', '内存', '硬盘', '', '5', '5', '6', '0.00', '8688.00', '0.00', '999', null, '1', '2017-08-29 16:36:15', 'Xinda/Product/2017-08-29/59a52750a8620.jpg', '0', '腰立辉', '2017-09-20 15:16:21');
INSERT INTO `zt_tp_product` VALUES ('wLU8hD9Yl054', '', '4', '9h0zez', 'fKAKiC', '1', '1', 'MacBook Air', '<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2008年2月19日<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Apple/3860362\" data-lemmaid=\"3860362\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Apple</a> 推出世界上最薄的笔记本，MacBook 家族（<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/MacBook\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">MacBook</a>，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/MacBook%20Pro\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">MacBook Pro</a>）的又一新成员MacBook Air。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">MacBook Air笔记本具有11.6寸和13.3寸两个尺寸，售价从6288元到12488元不等。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[1]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[1]_1366638\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\"> </a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">MacBook Air被美国知名媒体《商业内幕》在2013年即将结束之际纳入“本年度最具创新力的十大设备”。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background-image: url(\"https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png\"); background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; position: relative; text-indent: 0px;\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">外观设计</h2><a class=\"edit-icon j-edit-link\" data-edit-dl=\"3\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); display: block; float: right; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; padding-left: 24px; font-size: 12px; font-family: SimSun; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma\" style=\"font-family: baikeFont_layout; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; speak: none; line-height: 1; outline: 0px; margin: 0px 3px 0px 0px; vertical-align: text-bottom; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"></span>编辑</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">超轻薄</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Air的厚度甚至不如一本时尚杂志。MacBook Air的轻薄想必是人人皆知的，相比主流家用机型，仅重1.335kg的MacBook Air着实能让你轻松携带，拥有Air是那些追求便携的白领上班一族不二选择。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 250px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/d15717249f540112d40742a2?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MacBook Air(图2)\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 250px; height: 124px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://e.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D250/sign=d4b20f1cbc315c6047956ceabdb1cbe6/4610b912c8fcc3cef7b16a3a9245d688d43f2041.jpg\" alt=\"MacBook Air(图2)\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 250px; height: 124px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">MacBook Air(图2)</span></div>MBA的包装箱是黑色的，包装箱正上方印有半开启的MBA图片，包装箱前侧印有“MacBook Air”的字样，除此之外，再无其他标识，整体感觉很简洁。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">躺在黑色包装箱里的就是此次的主角——<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%B7%A7%E5%A4%BA%E5%A4%A9%E5%B7%A5\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">巧夺天工</a>的MBA，MBA尺寸为32.4cm x 22.7cm x 0.4-1.94cm，最薄处仅4mm，最厚处也只有1.8cm，将MBA拿到手里感觉很爽。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">MBA虽然很薄，但是拿在手里感觉很结实，上盖、腕托、机身底部各部位都没有丝毫松松垮垮的感觉，笔者在摸到M<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/1f569482e14cdca9f603a6ac?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MacBook Air(图3)\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 137px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=2773f130c93d70cf48faad0fc8dcd1ba/d043ad4bd11373f0da4fcc96a40f4bfbfbed0442.jpg\" alt=\"MacBook Air(图3)\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 137px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">MacBook Air(图3)</span></div>BA之前，很担心的一件事就是单手端起MBA机身会晃得厉害，不过实际情况令笔者很满意，单手端起MBA机身丝毫没有晃动的感觉。不过由此笔者也发现就一个问题，就是MBA虽然薄，但是并不轻，1.36Kg的重量在13.3寸笔记本中处于领先地位，如果和12.1寸或者更小尺寸的笔记本相比，MBA显得有些沉，单手端一段时间会感觉有些累。但是，2010年发布的11寸版本的1.06~1.08Kg（2011年）在11寸电脑上也特别轻。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">极其细腻，不是其他品牌金属<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%A3%A8%E7%A0%82\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">磨砂</a>质感可以比拟的。机身左侧设计有电源接口、一个<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/USB3.0\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">USB3.0</a>接口、和一个音频输入和输出接口，另外在音频接口右侧的是一个外置小MIC，这个小MIC上面遍布着密密麻麻的小孔，这都是拜激光光束的精细雕琢所赐，既不影响整体美观度，又达到了作用。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[4]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[4]_1366638\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\"> </a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">全机总重</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">由于新Air采用与上一代基本相同的模具，在重量上依旧保持了Air一贯的极致轻薄的风格。称重中裸机重量为1.33kg，旅行重量为1.52kg，携带起来还是相当方便的。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">散热布局</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/a1ec08fa513d2697fb02adaa55fbb2fb4216d870?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"外观\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 146px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=6d108ed08a82b90139adc431438fa97e/a1ec08fa513d2697fb02adaa55fbb2fb4216d870.jpg\" alt=\"外观\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 146px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">外观</span></div>苹果的风格我们都懂的，正因为这样独树一帜的设计成就了苹果今天的辉煌。散热设计在苹果的笔记本产品一贯的风格是后置的散热方式，后置散热窗包括进风风道窗和出风风道窗，从整机运行的发热走向来看，右侧为进风风道，左侧为出风风道。由于苹果产品转轴对视线的遮挡，成功的隐藏的散热窗的位置，从而使整机在外型上更为简洁唯美。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">屏幕特点</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">MacBook Air采用了13.3英寸1440×900分辨率的TN液晶屏，显示效果较常见的家用机要好上不少，没有普通家用机屏幕过亮或偏色等情况。可视角度方面，Air在所有的笔记本产品中也是中高水平，基本可以达到160度左右无色差显示。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">键盘特点</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/0e2442a7d933c8958bb23d8cd11373f08302007c?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"键盘\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 146px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=cf3b410fa786c9170c03553bf93f70c6/0e2442a7d933c8958bb23d8cd11373f08302007c.jpg\" alt=\"键盘\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 146px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">键盘</span></div>MacBook Air也采用一贯的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%B7%A7%E5%85%8B%E5%8A%9B%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">巧克力键盘</a>，触感和弹性都还比较适中，使用起来还是比较舒适的。另外新款Air的键盘采用了白色的背光，在夜晚使用不但漂亮异常而且实用性也很大。苹果的键盘一向耐磨性比较强，其出色的蚀刻技术的是保证键盘字迹在使用长久后依然保持清晰可见的重要原因，新Air也采用了蚀刻技术，想必在使用长久后字迹也依然会保持清晰。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">显示效果</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Air的屏幕对色彩的还原力还是相当不错的，将桌面的绿草背景渲染<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/5ab5c9ea15ce36d37155055238f33a87e950b17b?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"2013版MacBook Air\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 164px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://e.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=f340a28dabec8a13101a50e2c7029157/5ab5c9ea15ce36d37155055238f33a87e950b17b.jpg\" alt=\"2013版MacBook Air\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 164px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">2013版MacBook Air</span></div>的十分鲜活，比普通家用机型真的是逼真许多。而且在左右转动的情况下，屏幕依然能够保持这种较好的表现，与Pro对比丝毫不落于下风。得益于它1440×900较高的分辨率，图标边缘基本没有颗粒感，显示上也比2012年及之前发布的Pro精细许多。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"4\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub1366638_4\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"产品功能\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background-image: url(\"https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png\"); background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; position: relative; text-indent: 0px;\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">产品功能</h2><a class=\"edit-icon j-edit-link\" data-edit-dl=\"4\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); display: block; float: right; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; padding-left: 24px; font-size: 12px; font-family: SimSun; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma\" style=\"font-family: baikeFont_layout; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; speak: none; line-height: 1; outline: 0px; margin: 0px 3px 0px 0px; vertical-align: text-bottom; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"></span>编辑</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/834344afe241ddc2fbed50ac?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MacBook Air(图4)\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 137px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://g.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=2acf163319d8bc3ec20801c8b28ba6c8/80cb39dbb6fd526696589f1dab18972bd4073643.jpg\" alt=\"MacBook Air(图4)\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 137px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">MacBook Air(图4)</span></div>MBA虽然很薄，依然内置了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iSight\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iSight</a>摄像头和全向MIC，结合<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iChat\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iChat</a>或者其他即时通讯软件使用，可以给沟通带来很大的方便。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">按键方面MBA设计比较简洁，除了电源开关没有设计任何其他的快捷键，这也是Mac笔记本一向的设计风格。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">键盘及触摸板</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">MBA是13.3寸宽屏笔记本，对于13寸宽屏本来说，设计全尺寸键盘并不是什么困难的事情，对于MBA来说，困难之处是如何既不影响机身的薄，也不影响按键的手感。如果仔细观察，大家可以发现MBA的键盘整体是凹陷下去的，这样可以保证按键和键盘边框处在同一水平面的情况下具有一定的键程，笔者经过实际使用发现MBA键盘的手感和MacBook以及<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iMac\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iMac</a>配备的键盘手感都是一样的，按键很轻松，打起字来也比较舒服。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/95afee1f8ec7e092e1fe0bf3?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"键盘 触控板\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 165px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://e.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=63c4ad3e252dd42a5b0906a9333a5b2f/b90e7bec54e736d19bc0745f9b504fc2d4626992.jpg\" alt=\"键盘 触控板\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 165px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">键盘 触控板</span></div>其实MBA的键盘最大的特色是采用了背光灯的设计，带有环境光敏感元件，可以根据环境光的亮度来自动调整屏幕和键盘背光灯的亮度，这样在环境光比较昏暗的地方也可以看清键盘的字了，而且还不用自己去手动调节，比某些产品在屏幕上边框设计夜视灯要方便得多。MBA的触控板面积比较大，支持多触点技术，通过这项技术，开合、轻扫或旋转手指就能够可缩放文本、浏览相册或调整图像，这一手势输入技术已经在iPhone和<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPod%20Touch\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPod Touch</a>中得以成功应用，这次引入到MBA中，也是给笔记本带来了一项非常新颖的技术。为了实现这一手势输入技术，MBA配备了一颗Broadcom BCM5974触摸屏控制芯片，通过这一芯片，可以用触摸板来模拟触摸屏幕的效果，有机会大家可以到苹果体验店亲自体验一下这一技术，非常有意思。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">电源适配器</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/9358d109b3de9c8263ef3eb46f81800a19d84307?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"电源适配器\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 220px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=f9815ea42ddda3cc0fe4bf2231e83905/9358d109b3de9c8263ef3eb46f81800a19d84307.jpg\" alt=\"电源适配器\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 220px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">电源适配器</span></div>Mac电脑的电源插孔采用了安全插孔的设计方式，这种适配器称为MagSafe电源适配器，适配器接头和机身的插孔主要是靠磁铁的吸力结合在一起的，意外碰到的时候只会是适配器接头脱落而不至连累机器跌落。MBA为了照顾到小巧的机身，安全插孔的方向相对于MacBook的插孔已经旋转了90度。苹果笔记本一般会有两个适配器，一个是日常使用的标准适配器，一个是和数码产品适配器一样的便携式适配器（MBA只有一个便携式适配器），下图是苹果产品的一系列适配器，从上到下依次是iPhone (5瓦)、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPod\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPod</a> (8瓦)、MacBook Air (45瓦)、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/MacBook\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">MacBook</a> (60瓦)和<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/MacBook%20Pro\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">MacBook Pro</a>(85瓦)，我们可以看到，MBA不仅机身小巧，就连适配器的体积也要比MacBook和MacBook Pro的适配器小一圈。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">可升级性</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">MBA的可升级性是其软肋之一，由于为了追求极致轻薄，MBA在努力地将一切可集成的配件到主板上，不能集成的配件则采用软排线来进行连接以减小占用的空间，因此MBA很难进行升级。首先，MBA的所有配件都是位于机身内部的，要想升级要将机器后盖拆开，其次，MBA的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/CPU\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">CPU</a>、内存等都是集成在主板上的，个人用户是无法进行升级的。不过MBA的配置虽然不是很强，但是基本可以满足大多数应用需求，而且几乎已经达到了满足当前散热条件下的最高性能。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">周边配件</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 119px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/b8405490ac5ae5b4a977a4b0?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MacBook Air(图10)\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 119px; height: 220px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=9364e6f63bc79f3d8be1e3328aa0cdbc/d01373f082025aaffe56ddc2fbedab64034f1a56.jpg\" alt=\"MacBook Air(图10)\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 119px; height: 220px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">MacBook Air(图10)</span></div>1、牛皮纸袋状<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%86%85%E8%83%86%E5%8C%85\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">内胆包</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">在美国的发布会上<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B9%94%E5%B8%83%E6%96%AF\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">乔布斯</a>是从一个牛皮纸袋中拿出MBA的，这一举动非常酷，不仅给现场的观众也给稍后看到报道的用户很大的震撼，随后推出的MBA广告也是结合牛皮纸带来作的，让我们不得不佩服苹果策划人员的无限创意。为了将这一想法推向现实，Jona Bechtolt和Claire L. Evans设计了这个纯手工打造的牛皮纸袋状内胆包，是不是比普通的内胆包要酷得多？</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/SuperDrive\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">SuperDrive</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">SuperDrive是一个USB接口的外置DVD<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%88%BB%E5%BD%95%E5%85%89%E9%A9%B1\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">刻录光驱</a>，这个外置光驱的特点是无需笨重的电源适配器，只需要一根USB连接线就可以直接连接MBA，实现光盘播放或者刻录功能。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">3、USB以太网<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%BD%AC%E6%8E%A5%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">转接器</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">MBA太薄了，甚至连很常见的网卡接口也省略了，好在苹果还为MBA准备了USB到以太网接口的转换器，在没有无线局域网络的环境中也不会手足无措。 （仅第一代）</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">4、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/MagSafe\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">MagSafe</a>飞行电<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/3bc6f750817050651038c2b1?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MacBook Air(图11)\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 135px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://e.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=b352be011f30e924cba49b337c096e66/f7246b600c3387445fa28c75510fd9f9d72aa050.jpg\" alt=\"MacBook Air(图11)\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 135px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">MacBook Air(图11)</span></div>源适配器</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">MagSafe飞行电源适配器主要是位经常飞来飞去的空中超人准备的，将它插入飞机座位上的电源端口，可在整个飞行期间为你的MacBook Air供电，这样在飞机上也不会耽误工作。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">5、Micro-DVI至视频MBA机身上配有一个micro-DVI接口，通过转接线可连接到DVI或者VGA接口的外接显示设备，Micro-DVI至DVI和Micro-DVI至<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/VGA/258838\" data-lemmaid=\"258838\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">VGA</a>接口的转接线属于标准配置，不需要单独购买。（仅第一代）</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">6、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Time%20Capsule\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Time Capsule</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Time Capsule是一个无线<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%87%E4%BB%BD\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">备份</a>装置，通过<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Leopard/11814\" data-lemmaid=\"11814\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Leopard</a>系统中的Time Machine功能可以自动所有内容，这个设备是同时支持<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Mac%20OS\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Mac OS</a>系统和Windows系统，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Windows\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Windows</a>系统虽然没有Time Machine功能，但是可以通过拖拽的方式实现数据备份。Time Capsule有2TB和3TB两种规格供选择。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">7、其他</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">除了以上配件，苹果还提供了一些通用的配件供选择<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/4e83cb62596e73e4e7113ab2?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MacBook Air(图12)\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 146px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://e.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=d0a841f37bcb0a4681228c3b5b62f63e/b3b7d0a20cf431ad17b4e0304b36acaf2edd9851.jpg\" alt=\"MacBook Air(图12)\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 146px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">MacBook Air(图12)</span></div>，具体如下所示:</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">AirPort Extreme 基站 (MA073CH/A )</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">AirPort Express 基站，配有 AirTunes (M9470CH/A )</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Apple 无线键盘 (M9270CH/A )</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Apple 无线 Mighty Mouse (MB111CH/A )</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Apple USB调制解调器(MA034Z/A)</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Apple USB Ethernet Adapter</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Apple Mini DisplayPort to DVI Adapter （仅第三代）</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Apple Mini DisplayPort to VGA Adapter （仅第三代）</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"5\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub1366638_5\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"操作环境\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background-image: url(\"https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png\"); background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; position: relative; text-indent: 0px;\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">操作环境</h2><a class=\"edit-icon j-edit-link\" data-edit-dl=\"5\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); display: block; float: right; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; padding-left: 24px; font-size: 12px; font-family: SimSun; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma\" style=\"font-family: baikeFont_layout; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; speak: none; line-height: 1; outline: 0px; margin: 0px 3px 0px 0px; vertical-align: text-bottom; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"></span>编辑</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/d7c9ca3fa2c932fb7d1e71b3?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MacBook Air(图13)\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 146px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://f.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=c24c06d676c6a7efbd26af24cdfbafe9/94cad1c8a786c9175a63f130c93d70cf3bc75752.jpg\" alt=\"MacBook Air(图13)\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 146px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">MacBook Air(图13)</span></div>电压：100 至 240伏特交流电</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">频率：50 至 60Hz操作温度：10℃ 至 35℃（50°F 至 95°F ）</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">存放温度：-24℃ 至 45℃（-13°F 至 113° F ）</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">相对湿度：0% 至 90% 间，非冷凝状态</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">最高操作高度：3,000 米（10,000 英尺）</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">最高储存高度：4,500 米（15,000 英尺）</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">最高装运高度：10,667 米（35,000 英尺）</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"6\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub1366638_6\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"市场评价\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background-image: url(\"https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png\"); background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; position: relative; text-indent: 0px;\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">市场评价</h2><a class=\"edit-icon j-edit-link\" data-edit-dl=\"6\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); display: block; float: right; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; padding-left: 24px; font-size: 12px; font-family: SimSun; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma\" style=\"font-family: baikeFont_layout; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; speak: none; line-height: 1; outline: 0px; margin: 0px 3px 0px 0px; vertical-align: text-bottom; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"></span>编辑</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2012年7月美国科技博客网站<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/BusinessInsider\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">BusinessInsider</a>评选出本世纪迄今十款最重要电子产品，MacBook Air榜上有名。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2013款Macbook Air的外观同前作没有多少区别，但这款产品真正的变革源自内在。新款Macbook Air内置了英特尔最新的Haswell<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">处理器</a>，在计算机性能得到大幅提升的情况下却没有损失一点电池续航时间。有数据显示，13英寸2013款Macbook Air的电池续航时间最高可以达到惊人的12个小时。</div></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background-image: url(\"https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png\"); background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; position: relative; text-indent: 0px;\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">发展史</h2><a class=\"edit-icon j-edit-link\" data-edit-dl=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); display: block; float: right; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; padding-left: 24px; font-size: 12px; font-family: SimSun; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma\" style=\"font-family: baikeFont_layout; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; speak: none; line-height: 1; outline: 0px; margin: 0px 3px 0px 0px; vertical-align: text-bottom; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"></span>编辑</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2008年2月19日，苹果发布了当时全球最薄的笔记本电脑——MacBook Air （以下简称<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/MBA/5403996\" data-lemmaid=\"5403996\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">MBA</a>），这款13.3寸<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/LED\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">LED</a>屏幕笔记本最薄处仅4mm（平均厚度）。M<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 250px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/c2cec3fdfc039245349d30078094a4c27d1e258a?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mac Book Air\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 250px; height: 78px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://c.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D250/sign=be75d09059df8db1b82e7b613923dddb/c2cec3fdfc039245349d30078094a4c27d1e258a.jpg\" alt=\"Mac Book Air\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 250px; height: 78px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">Mac Book Air</span></div>BA所营造的视觉上的美感是很难用语言来形容的，MBA之所以能做到如此之薄主要源自于LED屏幕和特殊<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">处理器</a>的采用，MBA所采用的处理器是<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">英特尔</a>专门为苹果定制的，这种定制的处理器也属于<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%85%B7%E7%9D%BF2\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">酷睿2</a>系列，但是面积比标准的酷睿2处理器要小很多，功耗也要低不少，这种定制的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%85%B7%E7%9D%BF\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">酷睿</a>2处理器的应用，不仅有益于MBA的轻薄，也为MBA的良好散热提供了很好的支持，使MBA成为了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Mac\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Mac</a>系列电脑中发热量最小的电脑。首批发售的MBA配备的处理器型号是P7500，主频1.6GHz，具有4M二级缓存和800MHz前端总线，没有使用超低电压版处理器，估计苹果也是希望MBA在性能上也有可观的表现，并不想它沦为纯粹具有便携性的产品。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2010年10月，苹果发布第二代MBA。这次升级使MBA有了两种机型：传统的13.3英寸和新增的11.6英寸。它们的最大特点是用闪存代替硬盘，64GB～256GB的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%97%AA%E5%AD%98\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">闪存</a>被直接嵌入主板，节省了巨大空间来存放电池，这使13.3英寸机型的使用时间提升到7小时。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2011年7月，<a class=\"lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206\" title=\"Macbook Air\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/2267209/72ccb7776764264cb151b96b?fr=lemma&ct=cover\" target=\"_blank\" nslog-type=\"10000206\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 222px; border-bottom: 0px; margin: 10px 0px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right;\"><div class=\"album-wrap\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); width: 220px; height: 220px; overflow: hidden; position: relative;\"><img class=\"picture\" alt=\"Macbook Air\" src=\"https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=c14b6d8bd100baa1be2c40b97711b9b1/5bafa40f4bfbfbedf512961878f0f736afc31f09.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 220px; height: 220px; position: absolute; display: block;\"></div><div class=\"description\" style=\"padding: 8px 7px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; font-family: simSun; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(224, 224, 224); border-bottom-color: rgb(224, 224, 224); border-left-color: rgb(224, 224, 224); border-image: initial; border-top-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; text-indent: 0px; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;\">Macbook Air<span class=\"number\" style=\"display: inline; color: gray;\">(20张)</span></div><div class=\"albumBg\"><div class=\"albumBgFir\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(245, 245, 245) rgb(230, 230, 230) rgb(230, 230, 230); border-image: initial; height: 1px; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; width: 214px;\"></div><div class=\"albumBgSec\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(245, 245, 245) rgb(230, 230, 230) rgb(230, 230, 230); border-image: initial; height: 1px; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; width: 208px;\"></div></div></a> 苹果再次升级了MBA。全新的MBA搭载双核<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Intel%20Core%20i5\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Intel Core i5</a>和四核<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Core%20i7\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Core i7</a>处理器，在性能上实现了飞跃。这次升级后苹果的入门级笔记本<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Macbook\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Macbook</a>在官网中消失，Mac笔记本家族只剩下<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Macbook%20Air\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Macbook Air</a>和<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Macbook%20Pro\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Macbook Pro</a>。这也意味着MBA，一款超便携型笔记本，已经具有一般笔记本的性能和经济性。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2012年6月12日凌晨，苹果发布新款MacBook Air笔记本电脑（第四代）。根据资料，新版的MacBook Air 采用<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Intel\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Intel</a>第三代<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Core%20i5\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Core i5</a>双核处理器（22纳米，代号Ivy Bridge，主频为1.7GHz，共享3M的L3；主板集成低电压版的4GB 1600MHz DDR3L内存（可加钱升到8GB）；采用<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/SSD/5906\" data-lemmaid=\"5906\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">SSD</a>固态硬盘（SSD已固化到主板上），容量为64GB / 128GB（可以加钱升到256GB 或512GB），据说速度能达到500MB/s，不知是不是采用SandForce主控；集成<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Intel%20HD%20Graphics\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Intel HD Graphics</a> 4000显卡，提供2个USB 3.0接口和1个雷电（<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Thunderbolt\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Thunderbolt</a>）接口，支持Bluetooth 4.0，能续航5个小时，整机重量只<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 250px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/0/0d338744ebf81a4c308e3dc1d02a6059252da67e?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mac Book Air\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 250px; height: 121px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://b.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D250/sign=7eb10d1cbf99a9013f355c332d940a58/0d338744ebf81a4c308e3dc1d02a6059252da67e.jpg\" alt=\"Mac Book Air\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 250px; height: 121px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">Mac Book Air</span></div>有1.08 千克，最厚处仅有1.7 厘米。新版MacBook Air将于年内在国内上市，苹果中国官网公布MacBook Air 11英寸RMB6288起售；MacBook Air 13英寸RMB 6988元起售。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2013款11英寸除了搭载最新的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Haswell\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Haswell</a>处理器之外，苹果则是将续航作为了这次的又一大亮点。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">据苹果官方介绍，11寸版的MacBook Air续航时间可达9个小时，较前一代提升了将近一倍；13寸版本的更可达12小时。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">在效能方面，使用第四代<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Intel%20Core\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Intel Core</a>系列的MacBook Air，在图像处理效能上将有40%的增长，11寸版的与13寸版的将都有128GB和256GB SSD版本选择。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">在说到价格问题，11英寸新款Macbook Air的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%9B%BD%E8%A1%8C\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">国行</a>价格为6288元（128GB闪存）、7788元（256GB闪存）、13英寸价格为6988元（128GB闪存）、8488元（256GB闪存）。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a class=\"lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206\" title=\"新MacBook Air拆解\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Air/10576246/2267227/80cb39dbb6fd526604d70180ab18972bd50736a1?fr=lemma&ct=cover\" target=\"_blank\" nslog-type=\"10000206\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 222px; border-bottom: 0px; margin: 10px 0px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right;\"><div class=\"album-wrap\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); width: 220px; height: 165px; overflow: hidden; position: relative;\"><img class=\"picture\" alt=\"新MacBook Air拆解\" src=\"https://gss0.bdstatic.com/-4o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=b84088ae19d8bc3ec20801c8b28aa6c8/80cb39dbb6fd526604d70180ab18972bd50736a1.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 220px; height: 165px; position: absolute; display: block;\"></div><div class=\"description\" style=\"padding: 8px 7px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; font-family: simSun; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(224, 224, 224); border-bottom-color: rgb(224, 224, 224); border-left-color: rgb(224, 224, 224); border-image: initial; border-top-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; text-indent: 0px; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;\">新MacBook Air拆解<span class=\"number\" style=\"display: inline; color: gray;\">(20张)</span></div><div class=\"albumBg\"><div class=\"albumBgFir\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(245, 245, 245) rgb(230, 230, 230) rgb(230, 230, 230); border-image: initial; height: 1px; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; width: 214px;\"></div><div class=\"albumBgSec\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(245, 245, 245) rgb(230, 230, 230) rgb(230, 230, 230); border-image: initial; height: 1px; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; width: 208px;\"></div></div></a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">自苹果<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/MacBook/7817055\" data-lemmaid=\"7817055\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">MacBook</a>系列笔记本电脑于2005年面世以来，就成为苹果的“吸金”利器，在全球各个角落为<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">苹果公司</a>赚取了全年超过47.9%的净利润。新推出的MacBook Air外形上采用了最新的“楔形”设计，最厚处1.8厘米，最薄处为0.3厘米，由宽至窄的设计简单时尚。而且Mac Book Air将主板的位置放在了较厚的电脑后半侧，即使用手托着使用，手臂也能一直保持冰凉清爽。除此以外，对于要求电脑能够长时间待机的要求，Mac Book Air也成了不二之选，7小时的续航能力，30天待机，只需用手轻轻一碰，可以随时被唤醒。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">配备新一代 Intel 处理器、图形处理器与更快的闪存，这款日用笔记本电脑， 表现更显不凡。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2014年11月6日，苹果正在筹备且备受期待的Mac Book Air将搭载12英寸<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Retina/26862\" data-lemmaid=\"26862\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Retina</a> 显示屏。据称，可能会去掉散热器，或者设计会焕然一新等传言甚嚣尘上。据台湾地区媒体报道，新机型可能会在年内发售。</div></div>', '', '颜色', '尺寸', 'CPU', '内存', '硬盘', '', '5', '5', '6', '0.00', '6988.00', '0.00', '999', null, '0', null, 'Xinda/Product/2017-09-20/59c227d57efa7.jpg', '0', '腰立辉', '2017-09-20 16:33:25');
INSERT INTO `zt_tp_product` VALUES ('Zm58XGc1VRvd', '', '1', 'QaARsI', 'fKAKiC', '1', '1', ' iPad Pro', '<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPad Pro是苹果公司旗下ipad平板中的一个型号，2016年3月22日，在春季新品发布会上，</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C/6011224\" data-lemmaid=\"6011224\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">苹果</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">公司除了带来了小尺寸的iPhone之外，还对外发布了9.7英寸的iPad Pro，iPad Pro搭载A9x核心处理器芯片。</span><div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background: url(\"https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png\") rgb(255, 255, 255); position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">功能设置</h2><br></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 250px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iPad%20Pro/19468872/0/241f95cad1c8a786a8172db86009c93d70cf5042?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iPad Pro\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 250px; height: 97px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D250/sign=84ddb59797ef76c6d4d2fc2ead16fdf6/241f95cad1c8a786a8172db86009c93d70cf5042.jpg\" alt=\"iPad Pro\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 250px; height: 97px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">iPad Pro</span></div>016年3月21日，苹果公司推出9.7英寸iPad Pro，这是iPad Pro家族中第二个产品。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">新款iPad Pro质量为1磅，采用了“True Tone显示屏”，配置了1200万像素的摄像头，支持4K。该产品还拥有客户化的Smart键盘，支持<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Apple%20Pencil\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Apple Pencil</a>(苹果触控笔)。该产品配置4个扬声器，以及A9X处理器。这款产品显示屏的反光度比<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad%20Air%202\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPad Air 2</a>降低40%，亮度比iPad Air 2提升25%。另外，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%B0%E6%AC%BE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">新款</a>iPad Pro支持Night Shift，可以自测环境光，根据环境光冷暖，自我调节色调。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"2\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub20017555_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"版本价格\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background: url(\"https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png\") rgb(255, 255, 255); position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">版本价格</h2><br></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2016年3月新版，32GB 599美元，128GB 749美元。 该产品3月24日开始接受预定，并于3月31日<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">正式</a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8F%91%E5%94%AE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">发售</a>。首发中包括<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/1122445\" data-lemmaid=\"1122445\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">中国</a></div></div>', '', '颜色', '网路', '内存', '', '', '', '5', '5', '6', '0.00', '3788.00', '0.00', '999', null, '0', null, 'Xinda/Product/2017-09-20/59c21f372b30c.jpg', '0', '腰立辉', '2017-09-20 15:56:49');
INSERT INTO `zt_tp_product` VALUES ('AZp3TnX9Yzvb', '', '2', 'QaARsI', 'fKAKiC', '1', '1', 'iPad（第五代）', '<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">北<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iPad/9849885/0/08f790529822720e516f0e3a72cb0a46f31fab49?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"新iPad\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 163px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=6be6034443ed2e73f8e9812eb700a16d/08f790529822720e516f0e3a72cb0a46f31fab49.jpg\" alt=\"新iPad\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 163px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">新iPad</span></div>京时间2017年3月23日，苹果在官网上新了新款iPad ，新款iPad的高度为240 毫米(9.4英寸)，宽度为169.5 毫米(6.6英寸)，厚度为7.5 毫米(0.29英寸)。重量为469 克(1.03磅)，Cellular版为478 克(1.05磅)。采用Retina 显示屏，9.7 英寸 (对角线) LED 背光 Multi‑Touch 显示屏，采用 IPS 技术、2048 x 1536 像素分辨率，264 ppi，并且采用了防油渍防指纹涂层 。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">芯片方面，采用了64 位架构的 A9 芯片和嵌入式 M9 协处理器。后置摄像头支持800像素摄像头，支持1080p视频拍摄，支持拍摄120万像素拍照的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/FaceTime\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">FaceTime</a>HD 摄像头。内置了 32.4 瓦时锂聚合物充电电池。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">与此同时，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad%20Air%202\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPad Air 2</a>停止销售。</div>', '', '颜色', '网路', '内存', '', '', '', '5', '5', '6', '0.00', '3788.00', '0.00', '999', null, '0', null, 'Xinda/Product/2017-09-20/59c21e9a38f51.jpg', '0', '腰立辉', '2017-09-20 15:56:46');
INSERT INTO `zt_tp_product` VALUES ('JJt69FtNJDRl', '', '3', 'QaARsI', 'fKAKiC', '1', '1', 'iPad mini 4', '<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPad</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> mini 4已经上架</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%AE%98%E7%BD%91\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">官网</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">，有银色、灰色、金色三种配色，重量仅仅为298.8克，厚度为6.1毫米，容量大小为128GB，其WLAN版售价为3288元，其WLAN+Cellular版售价为4388元。2015年推出的iPad mini 4相对前代提升幅度显著，将会使用最新的A8</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[1]_16194633\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> 处理器，并且采用与</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad%20Air%202\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPad Air 2</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">类似的超薄设计，</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad%20mini%203\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPad mini 3</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">将会抛弃，整个阵营只留下它和</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad%20mini%202\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPad mini 2</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。</span><div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background: url(\"https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png\") rgb(255, 255, 255); position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">简介</h2><br></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iPad%20mini%204/16247716/0/4b90f603738da9778f09fac9b851f8198618e32a?fr=lemma&ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iPad mini4\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 172px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=adcee4bcd5c451daf2f60be986fc52a5/4b90f603738da9778f09fac9b851f8198618e32a.jpg\" alt=\"iPad mini4\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 172px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">iPad mini4</span></div>2015年推出的iPad mini 4不会有什么大的提升，将采用最新的A8<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">处理器</a>，并且采用与<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad%20Air%202\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPad Air 2</a>类似的超薄设计，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad%20mini%203\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPad mini 3</a>将会抛弃，整个阵营只留下它和iPad mini 2。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于iPad mini 4的变化，有外媒认为，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%206%20Plus\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPhone 6 Plus</a>在一定程度上抢走了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad%20mini\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPad mini</a>系列的用户，而<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C/6011224\" data-lemmaid=\"6011224\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">苹果</a>也开始将注意力放在了更大尺寸的平板上，所以iPad mini系列不会有太大的突破了。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">苹果第四代iPad mini可能会在年中的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/WWDC\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">WWDC</a> 2015开发者大会上与我们见面。苹果的第四代iPad mini 4将会很快发布，并且将配备A8处理器，支持802.11ac<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Wi-Fi\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Wi-Fi</a>。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"2\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub16194633_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"配置\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background: url(\"https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png\") rgb(255, 255, 255); position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">配置</h2><br></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPad mini 4完全可被称为苹果公司史上“最憋屈”的产品，发布会只提了一句“它变得更轻了”便算正式发布，与同期出场的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad%20Pro/1907532\" data-lemmaid=\"1907532\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPad Pro</a>相比，相当的不受重视。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但如果细琢磨，这款产品其实是不错的，相比上一代，它的外形小有改变，更轻薄的机身基本就是iPad Air 2的缩小版，厚度也与Air 2保持一致，仅有6.1毫米，重量也减轻到了298.8克，全层压显示屏、抗反射涂层等配置也是只有Air 2和iPad Pro才有的。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">mini 4的芯片是A8，虽然没有Air 2的A8X那么快，但也比上一代的A7快很多，它的摄像头也得到了升级，目前已经是800万像素，还加入了气压计。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最重要的是，这款产品也是2GB RAM。可以实现分屏操作等功能。相比iPad mini2到3代的微弱改进，可以说mini 4是很有诚意的。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">只是生不逢时，它赶上了大变革产品<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPad%20Pro/1907532\" data-lemmaid=\"1907532\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPad Pro</a>，目前苹果公司官网几乎都是关于后者的宣传，iPad mini 4或许会被更多用户购买，但在宣传上实在是低调。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"3\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub16194633_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"产品发布\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background: url(\"https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png\") rgb(255, 255, 255); position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">产品发布</h2><br></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2015年9月10日，苹果公司发布iPad mini4，售价为399美元。</div></div>', '', '颜色', '网路', '内存', '', '', '', '5', '5', '6', '0.00', '4388.00', '0.00', '999', null, '0', null, 'Xinda/Product/2017-09-20/59c21f2cbb68d.jpg', '0', '腰立辉', '2017-09-20 15:56:44');
INSERT INTO `zt_tp_product` VALUES ('w1ciEvv4RYxM', '', '1', 'Plxo5q', 'fKAKiC', '1', '1', 'iPhone 7', '<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone</a>&nbsp;7是<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Apple/3860362\" data-lemmaid=\"3860362\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Apple</a>（<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">苹果公司</a>）第10代手机，北京时间2016年9月8日凌晨1点在美国<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%97%A7%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1/29211\" data-lemmaid=\"29211\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">旧金山</a>比尔·格雷厄姆市政礼堂<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/2016%E5%B9%B4%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%A7%8B%E5%AD%A3%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E4%BC%9A\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">2016年苹果秋季新品发布会</a>上发布。<span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[1-3]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[1-3]_6542020\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPhone 7拥有金色、银色、玫瑰金色、黑色、亮黑色、红色(特别版，后增加)六种颜色。<span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[4]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[4]_6542020\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Home%E9%94%AE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Home键</a>有了全新的设计，添加了振动反馈。并且支持IP67防溅抗水防尘功能<span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[5]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[5]_6542020\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a>&nbsp;，前/后单摄像头，防抖功能，新增了速度更快的A10 Fusion<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">处理器</a>。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPhone 7取消了3.5mm耳机接口，推出新耳机<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Apple%20AirPods\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Apple AirPods</a>，采用W1芯片，有<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BC%A0%E6%84%9F%E5%99%A8/26757\" data-lemmaid=\"26757\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">传感器</a>，电池，都放在小小的耳机机身中。<span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[6]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[6]_6542020\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%207%20Plus\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 7 Plus</a>的电池容量只有2900<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/mAh\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">mAh</a>，相比<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%206%20Plus\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 6 Plus</a>上的2915mAh在容量上还小那么一点点，却能建立在更强悍的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/A10%20Fusion\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">A10 Fusion</a>处理器上多提供超过一个小时的续航时间,iPhone 7 Plus使用双摄像头。<span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[7]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[7]_6542020\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">新iPhone取消了16GB机型，最低存储容量为32GB，另外两个容量是128GB和256GB。</div>', '', '颜色', '内存', '', '', '', '', '5', '5', '6', '0.00', '6188.00', '0.00', '999', null, '0', '2017-08-29 17:02:59', 'Xinda/Product/2017-09-20/59c1d42cca65a.jpg', '0', '腰立辉', '2017-09-20 10:40:13');
INSERT INTO `zt_tp_product` VALUES ('5IaBVhuqmDFw', '', '2', 'Plxo5q', 'fKAKiC', '1', '1', 'iPhone 7 Plus', '<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPhone 7 Plus是苹果7升级版手机，北京时间2016年9月8日<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/2016%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%A7%8B%E5%AD%A3%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E4%BC%9A\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">2016苹果秋季新品发布会</a>上发布。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPhone 7 Plus屏幕大小5.5英寸，拥有双1200万像素摄像头，虚化效果自然，亮度提升了25%，色彩更佳。<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%89%AC%E5%A3%B0%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">扬声器</a>升级，采用上下立体声的扬声器。取消了3.5mm耳机接口， 推出全新耳机<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Apple%20AirPods\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Apple AirPods</a>。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2016年9月9日开启预约，9月16日正式开卖，中国首发。iPhone 7 Plus起价6388元。有银色、金色、玫瑰金、黑色、亮黑和红色。存储有32GB/128GB以及256GB可选。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2017年3月21日，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/2017%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%A5%E5%AD%A3%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E4%BC%9A\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">2017苹果春季新品发布会</a>发布，iPhone 7 Plus推出红色特别版提供128GB和256GB存储容量的机型，起售价为人民币6,188 元。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background-image: url(&quot;https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png&quot;); background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; position: relative; text-indent: 0px;\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">功能特征</h2><br></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">iPh<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 250px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iPhone%207%20Plus/15595891/0/10dfa9ec8a1363275f0713a69b8fa0ec09fac7b9?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iPhone7与iPhone7 Plus\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 250px; height: 91px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D250/sign=44e6eef0b919ebc4c478719cb227cf79/10dfa9ec8a1363275f0713a69b8fa0ec09fac7b9.jpg\" alt=\"iPhone7与iPhone7 Plus\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 250px; height: 91px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">iPhone7与iPhone7 Plus</span></div>one 7 Plus是双1200万像素<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%B4\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">摄像头</a>，虚化效果自然，在拍照界面就可以看到背景虚化的预览。亮度提升了25%，色彩更佳。扬声器升级，采用上下立体声的扬声器。取消了3.5mm耳机接口， 推出全新耳机<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Apple%20AirPods\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Apple AirPods</a>。续航5小时，带上耳机自动播放音乐，波束的麦克风效果更好，双击耳机开启<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Siri/32248\" data-lemmaid=\"32248\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Siri</a>，充电盒支持24小时续航，链接非常简单，只需要打开就可以让iPhone自动识别。采用W1芯片，有传感器，电池，都放在小小的耳机机身中。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[1]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[1]_15503430\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">新<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 250px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iPhone%207%20Plus/15595891/0/4a36acaf2edda3ccd1d74ea709e93901213f9202?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Apple AirPods\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 250px; height: 120px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D250/sign=c66d359363600c33f479d9cd2a4d5134/4a36acaf2edda3ccd1d74ea709e93901213f9202.jpg\" alt=\"Apple AirPods\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 250px; height: 120px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">Apple AirPods</span></div>版本的苹果iPhone 7 Plus除了处理器升级到<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/A10%20Fusion\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">A10 Fusion</a>，增加性能和续航之外，双摄像头成为主要的卖点。在新版本iPhone7中，操作系统<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iOS10\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iOS10</a>得以更新，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Siri/32248\" data-lemmaid=\"32248\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Siri</a>在App内得到了应用，同时系统中的智能家居<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/HomeKit\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">HomeKit</a>平台也成为一个亮点。苹果取消了3.5毫米的标准手机接口而推出了Lightning接口耳机，附送转接线，并且给了用户选择全新AirPods无线耳机的机会。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">取消3.5mm耳机接口；摄像头还是凸起；不支持快充功能；不支持双卡。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"2\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub15503430_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"改动对比\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background-image: url(&quot;https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png&quot;); background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; position: relative; text-indent: 0px;\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">改动对比</h2><br></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">i<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iPhone%207%20Plus/15595891/0/5ab5c9ea15ce36d3e52d97b832f33a87e950b108?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iPhone7 Plus\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 186px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=67383067a1ec8a13101a50e2c7029157/5ab5c9ea15ce36d3e52d97b832f33a87e950b108.jpg\" alt=\"iPhone7 Plus\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 186px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">iPhone7 Plus</span></div>Phone 7 Plus对于<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%207\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPhone 7</a>最大的改动来自于<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">处理器</a>和<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">内存</a>，iPhone 7将继续采用2GB内存，而iPhone 7 Plus的内存将提高到3GB。同时，两款iPhone 7和iPhone 7 Plus都将采用A10的移动<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">处理器</a>。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">经测试，iPhone 7和iPhone 7 Plus的性能差异并不大，响应和加载速度都差不多。苹果iPhone 7 Plus配备更高容量的运行内存是为了改进双镜头的图像处理，或许在处理更繁杂的任务时才能真正体现3GB内存的优势。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"3\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub15503430_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); posi