601a18b87d6277f9198f88d20381f30e824fcf9?fr=lemma&amp;ct=cover\" target=\"_blank\" nslog-type=\"10000206\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 222px; border-bottom: 0px; margin: 10px 0px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right;\"><div class=\"album-wrap\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); width: 220px; height: 144px; overflow: hidden; position: relative;\"><img class=\"picture\" alt=\"iPhone 6s Plus\" src=\"https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=743e61d407b30f24319aeb01f894d192/8601a18b87d6277f9198f88d20381f30e824fcf9.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; width: 220px; height: 144px; position: absolute; display: block;\"></div><div class=\"description\" style=\"padding: 8px 7px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; font-family: simSun; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; border-right-color: rgb(224, 224, 224); border-bottom-color: rgb(224, 224, 224); border-left-color: rgb(224, 224, 224); border-image: initial; border-top-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; text-indent: 0px; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;\">iPhone 6s Plus<span class=\"number\" style=\"display: inline; color: gray;\">(4张)</span></div><div class=\"albumBg\"><div class=\"albumBgFir\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(245, 245, 245) rgb(230, 230, 230) rgb(230, 230, 230); border-image: initial; height: 1px; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; width: 214px;\"></div><div class=\"albumBgSec\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(245, 245, 245) rgb(230, 230, 230) rgb(230, 230, 230); border-image: initial; height: 1px; margin: 0px auto; overflow: hidden; width: 208px;\"></div></div></a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Home 键返回的次数也越来越频繁，似乎要成为世界第一难题，但是苹果的存在让产品和用户之间最微小的摩擦也完全剔除了。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Business Insider：</span>苹果的 3D Touch 会让操作变得流畅自然并且速度更快，但其并非是一项突破性的交互，只是可以让你在很多地方节省时间而已。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">BGR：</span>苹果 iPhone 6s 的五大遗憾</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">第一 iPhone6s 和 iPhone6s Plus 在厚度上均有增加，苹果每年都会推出更薄的产品，3D Touch 的出现让我的手机变厚了。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">第二是电池容量没长进，虽然 A9 处理器和其他组件的的功效都下降了，软件也进行了优化，但唯独电池容量没有增加。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">第三分辨率没有像之前期待的得到提升，虽然苹果的 Retina 屏幕的分辨率足够，但 326ppi 的 iPhone6s 和同类型的产品相比还是太低。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">第四摄像头有凸起还没有解决，“这种可怕的妥协让手机看起来相当丑陋”。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">第五起步容量依然是 16GB，但是这对不少人来说已经不够了，迫使他们不得不花更多的钱买更大容量的 iPhone。</div></div>', '', '颜色', '内存', '', '', '', '', '1', '5', '6', '0.00', '5388.00', '0.00', '999', null, '0', '2017-08-29 17:04:03', 'Xinda/Product/2017-08-29/59a52df498e5f.jpg', '0', '腰立辉', '2017-09-20 15:09:37');
INSERT INTO `zt_tp_product` VALUES ('Nksye5laKW6M', null, '5', 'Plxo5q', 'fKAKiC', '1', '1', 'iPhone 8', '<div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iPhone</a>&nbsp;8是<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Apple/3860362\" data-lemmaid=\"3860362\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Apple</a>（<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">苹果公司</a>）第11代手机，北京时间2017年9月13日凌晨1点，在<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Apple%20Park\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Apple Park</a>新总部的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8F%B2%E8%92%82%E5%A4%AB%C2%B7%E4%B9%94%E5%B8%83%E6%96%AF%E5%89%A7%E9%99%A2\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">史蒂夫·乔布斯剧院</a>举行苹果新品发布会上发布的年度旗舰手机。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2017年9月13日，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/2017%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%A7%8B%E5%AD%A3%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E4%BC%9A\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">2017苹果秋季新品发布会</a>发布了iPhone 8，支持无线充电，分为64GB、256GB两个版本，699美元起售。</div></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" simhei,=\"\" verdana;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;\"=\"\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">外形</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">i<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 120px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iPhone%208/824799/0/279759ee3d6d55fb8bbcb23666224f4a20a4ddac?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 120px; height: 220px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=8046bbb0fd03738dda4a0b20831bb073/279759ee3d6d55fb8bbcb23666224f4a20a4ddac.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 120px; height: 220px;\"></a></div>Phone8与iPhone7的正脸一致，太空级别铝质设计，前后均为玻璃镜面，防水、防尘，还支持无线充电。背面玻璃机身，可选颜色：金色、银色以及深空灰。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" simhei,=\"\" verdana;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;\"=\"\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">性能</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"wor