 both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" simhei,=\"\" verdana;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;\"=\"\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">音质</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">多屏降噪。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"2_4\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub20856033_2_4\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"屏幕\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" simhei,=\"\" verdana;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;\"=\"\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">屏幕</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">视频编码器，对4K进行实时优化。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"2_5\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub20856033_2_5\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"售价\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" simhei,=\"\" verdana;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;\"=\"\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">售价</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">iPhone8国行售价5888元起，相比iPhone7系列上市的价格，iPhone8涨了500块钱。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">iPhone 8的64GB和256GB售价分别为5888元和7188元，iPhone 8 Plus的64GB和256GB售价分别为6688元和7988元。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"></span></div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"2_6\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub20856033_2_6\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"参数\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" simhei,=\"\" verdana;=\"\" text-indent:=\"\" 0px;\"=\"\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">参数</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">1200万像素摄像头，F1.8超大光圈设计，采用全新的镜头模组。配备了全新的视频编码器，拥有更快的视频帧速率，支持拍摄60帧的4K视频和全高清分辨率的慢速视频。</div></div></div>', '', '颜色', '内存', '', '', '', null, null, '5', '6', '0.00', '0.00', '0.00', null, null, '