" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">面积</span>: 35.7*24.3厘米（15.4寸）, 39.2*26.5厘米（17寸）</div></li><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">厚度</span>: 2.59厘米</div></li><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">固件接口</span>: 可扩展固件接口</div></li><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">机身</span>：精密铝合金一体式机身（15.4寸），铝合金（17寸）</div></li></ul><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">2006年10月24日升级款</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">Apple发布了使用<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">英特尔</a><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%85%B7%E7%9D%BF\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">酷睿</a>2双核</span>处理器的MacBook Pro笔记本电脑。此代产品使用的处理器为<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">英特尔</a>酷睿双核。搭载Yonah代号的双核心<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">处理器</a>用以接替Banias/Dothan代号的<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">奔腾M</span>处理器。此处理器搭配<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/SSE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">SSE</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/SSE2\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">SSE2</a>、与<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/SSE3\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">SSE3</a>技术，2 MB的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%8C%E7%BA%A7%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">二级缓存</a>与<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E5%8C%96%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">虚拟化技术</a>。</div><ul class=\"custom_dot para-list list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 2em; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">中央处理器</a>升级到了2.4 GHz（15英寸）和2.5 GHz（15英寸、17英寸均有）。<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">苹果公司</a>称其运行比原来快39%。</div></li><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\">内存容量扩大。标准配置中，2.16GHz配1GB，2.33 GHz&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/CPU\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">CPU</a>配2GB容量的667MHz DDR2 SDRAM内存，而且均可最大可以拓展到3GB。</div></li><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\">硬盘：15英寸的两种型号配120G，17英寸型号配160G，并均可拓展到200G。</div></li><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\">显卡：使用ATI Mobility Radeon X1600。2.33 GHz&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/CPU\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">CPU</a>配256MB图形缓存。</div></li><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\">配有<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%81%AB%E7%BA%BF\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">火线</a>800和400接口各一个。15英寸2个USB接口，17英寸3个USB接口。</div></li><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\">无线网络：搭载54 Mbps的AirPort Extreme（IEEE802.11n）与蓝牙2.0+<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/EDR\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">EDR</a>。并在之后提供了用于激活802.11n的收费补丁。</div></li></ul><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"1_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub89160_1_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"第二代\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; text-indent: 0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">第二代</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">2008年第二代MacBook Pro相比较第一代产品而言改进主要有：</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">从设计上，使用计算机数控机床（<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/CNC\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">CNC</a>）用来制造<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%88%AA%E5%A4%A9%E9%A3%9E%E6%9C%BA\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">航天飞机</a>零件工艺将整块铝合金材质切削成一体成型机身，使部件的数量和拼接处大大减少，同时更耐震。使用<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/LED\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">LED</a>显示（仅背光）面板，增加了续航时间的同时，还减少了笔记本的厚度。显示器的玻璃也采用了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iMac\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">iMac</a>的设计，扩展到了边框外延（之后还增加了高分辨率防眩光屏幕的选项）。触控板也有了很大改进，除了之前的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Multi-Touch\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">Multi-Touch</a>技术，还将触控区域与按键功能融合在一起，平滑的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%A3%A8%E7%A0%82%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">磨砂玻璃</a>减少了摩擦力且更加耐磨。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/MacBook%20Pro/1609153/0/64380cd7912397dd891aec435b82b2b7d0a28711?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"此代MacBook Pro采用的触摸板\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 164px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://a.hiphotos.baidu.com/baike/s%3D220/sign=671461d3442309f7e36faa10420f0c39/64380cd7912397dd891aec435b82b2b7d0a28711.jpg\" alt=\"此代MacBook Pro采用的触摸板\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 164px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">此代MacBook Pro采用的触摸板</span></div></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">从功能上，同时采用了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/NVIDIA\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">NVIDIA</a>&nbsp;GeForce 9400M集成图形处理器和NVIDIA 9600M GT独立图形处理器<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8F%8C%E6%98%BE%E5%8D%A1\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">双显卡</a>。可以互相切换使用，已达到更高性能或更省电的不同功用。经过软件优化新的NVIDIA图形处理器能让高清视频更加顺畅的播放。<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%83%8C%E5%85%89%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">背光键盘</a>采用了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/MacBook%20Air\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">MacBook Air</a>的设计，更加贴合指尖触感。有趣的是苹果曾在2010年版的MacBook Air中取消了背光键盘，但在2011又再次使用回背光键盘。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">在环境保护上，经过了新的设计和材料上的选择，MacBook Pro不再含有汞、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%A0%B7\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">砷</a>、BFR溴化阻燃剂、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/PVC\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">PVC</a>等有害物质，采用了高度可回收铝合金与玻璃材质外壳，在节能方面也更加出色。因此新款的MacBook Pro获得了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E4%B9%8B%E6%98%9F\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">能源之星</a>认证和<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/EPEAT\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">EPEAT</a>金级认证。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[3]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[3]_89160\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">规格</div><ul class=\"custom_dot para-list list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 2em; padding: 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">处理器</span>: 2.4GHz/2.66 GHz的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">英特尔</a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%85%B7%E7%9D%BF2\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">酷睿2</a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8F%8C%E6%A0%B8%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">双核处理器</a>。</div></li><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">记忆体</span>: 2 GB（2×1 GB）或4 GB（2×2 GB）的1066 MHz&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/DDR3%20SDRAM\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">DDR3 SDRAM</a></div></li><li class=\"list-dot list-dot-paddingleft\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">屏幕</span>: 1440*900像素的15.4寸<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/LED\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">LED</a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B6%B2%E6%99%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%99%A8\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-l