ent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Thunderbolt 技术通过同一接口提供两条<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BF%A1%E9%81%93\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">信道</a>，双向吞吐能力达到 10Gbps。它可以让你通过一个小巧的端口，以菊花链方式串接一台显示器和多达六部设备，包括 Promise Pegasus 这样的高性能存储解决方案。你会发现，数据传输速率快达 FireWire 800 的 12 倍。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[1]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[1]_9958047\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">OS X Server</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Mac mini Server安装了苹果公司专为服务器配备的OS X Server系统，使得建立和管理服务器变得更简单方便。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[1]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[1]_9958047\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"2\" class=\"le