INSERT INTO `zt_tp_product` VALUES ('RGOXQ8qy6ehI', null, '4', 'DGePKX', 'fKAKiC', '1', '1', 'Magic Trackpad', '<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Magic Trackpad是一个搭载</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%9A%E7%82%B9%E8%A7%A6%E6%8E%A7\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">多点触控</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/multi-touch\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">multi-touch</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">）技术的</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%A7%A6%E6%8E%A7%E6%9D%BF\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">触控板</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。于2010年7月27日发布。对比当时的</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Macbook%20Pro\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Macbook Pro</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的触控版，面积大了80%。PC和Mac和linux事实上都可以使用。2015年10月13日，苹果发布了Magic Trackpad 2，Magic Trackpad就不再售卖。</span><div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background: url(&quot;https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png&quot;) rgb(255, 255, 255); position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">介绍</h2><br></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Magic Trackpad 的表面使用和MacBook Pro上触控版相同的玻璃材质。<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/Magic%20Trackpad/8369325/0/b29f8282c11b4ffe6c8119a1?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Magic Trackpad\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 135px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=007bd002fbf2b211e02e824cfa806511/ae51f3deb48f8c5484ad735e3a292df5e0fe7f40.jpg\" alt=\"Magic Trackpad\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 135px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">Magic Trackpad</span></div>外壳也是和MacBook Pro相同的铝合金材质。比2009年款的MacBook Pro的触控版大了80%。曾经是Apple 制造的最大的Multi-Touch 触控板。但之后Magic Trackpad 2和2016年款的MacBook打破了这一纪录。使用5号电池进行供电，用蓝牙与电脑进行配对。和Apple Wireless Keyboard放在一起的时候，高度是一样的。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">和Macbook Pro触控版一样，这个触控版是单键触控版，整个触控版都可以进行按压操作，就像“<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%B7%B3%E6%B0%B4%E6%9D%BF\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">跳水板</a>”。辅助按键（右键）一般用双指按来进行操作。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"2\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub4024021_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"操作方式\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-2\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; overflow: hidden; border-left: 12px solid rgb(79, 156, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 22px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; margin: 35px 0px 15px -30px; background: url(&quot;https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/normal/resource/img/paraTitle-line_c5e6d61.png&quot;) rgb(255, 255, 255); position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><h2 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 0px 18px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); float: left; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 400; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">操作方式</h2><a class=\"edit-icon j-edit-link\" data-edit-dl=\"2\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); display: block; float: right; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; padding-left: 24px; font-size: 12px; font-family: SimSun; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma\" style=\"font-family: baikeFont_layout; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; speak: none; line-height: 1; outline: 0px; margin: 0px 3px 0px 0px; vertical-align: text-bottom; color: rgb(170, 170, 170);\"></span>编辑</a></div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"2_1\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub4024021_2_1\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"轻点\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">轻点</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在 Multi-Touch 表面随处点按，可实现单击和双击。或在系统偏好设置中启用\"轻拍点按”，轻拍触控板一次或两次就可实现单击和双击。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"2_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub4024021_2_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"滚动\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">滚动</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使用双指在 Multi-Touch 表面沿着纵向、横向或对角线等任何方向进行滚动操作。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"2_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub4024021_2_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"轻扫\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: r