: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>的A9处理器同样也是两个版本，其中代号为S8003的是<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A7%AF%E7%94%B5\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">台积电</a>(<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/TSMC\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">TSMC</a>)版本，代号S8000的则是三星(<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Samsung\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Samsung</a>)版本。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[4]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[4]_19921660\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"4_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub19921660_4_2\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"内存\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; text-indent: 0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">内存</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>的处理器主频和内存容量方面，该机的内存容量确实2GB。该机所配的A9处理器主频为1.85GHz,和<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%206s\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 6s</a>的A9处理器主频一样，并没有就此性能有所缩水，而内存容量则为1.96GB，与安兔兔公布的2GB内存基本吻合。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[4]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[4]_19921660\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"4_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub19921660_4_3\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"系统\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; text-indent: 0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">系统</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>采用<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iOS%209.3\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iOS 9.3</a>（最新版为<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iOS/45705\" data-lemmaid=\"45705\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iOS</a>11.0）操作系统，新系统主要带来了全新的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Night%20Shift\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Night Shift</a>功能以及备忘录加密功能等。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[5]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[5]_19921660\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Night Shift</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Night%20Shift\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Night Shift</a>模式是iOS9.3的一个重点功能<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iPhone%20SE/19420249/0/9f2f070828381f30aa4f6837ae014c086f06f0de?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iOS9.3\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 154px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=01cc099dcf95d143de76e32143f18296/9f2f070828381f30aa4f6837ae014c086f06f0de.jpg\" alt=\"iOS9.3\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 154px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">iOS9.3</span></div>，能够根据实际环境光线来调整屏幕背光。当环境光很黑暗时，Night Shift模式会让屏幕背光降到一个合适的亮度，更重要的是滤蓝光，更好地保护眼睛。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[5]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[5]_19921660\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">其它</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">除了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Night%20Shift\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Night Shift</a>模式之外，iOS9.3还将为备忘录加入密码功能，用户可以为自己的备忘录进行加密，以确保自己的隐私不被窥视。这个密码同样支持指纹解锁。此外Health应用中有了更多支持的App，还有新的新闻应用（中文版不出意外依旧与此无关）以及教育应用，其中这个教育应用在国内的实用性几乎没有。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[5]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[5]_19921660\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"4_4\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub19921660_4_4\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"拍照\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; text-indent: 0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">拍照</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">iP<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iPhone%20SE/19420249/0/d31b0ef41bd5ad6ed306905886cb39dbb7fd3c80?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"iPhoneSE-摄像头\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 125px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=9c9a108bb4de9c82a265fe8d5c8080d2/d31b0ef41bd5ad6ed306905886cb39dbb7fd3c80.jpg\" alt=\"iPhoneSE-摄像头\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 125px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">iPhoneSE-摄像头</span></div>hone&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">SE</a>将摄像头配置升级至与<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%206s\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 6s</a>同级水准，后置摄像头像素提升至f 2.2光圈、1200万像素，闪光灯仍采用True&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Tone\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Tone</a>双色温补光灯，同时前置镜头也能像<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%206s\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 6s</a>那样，以显示屏显示True&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Tone\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Tone</a>颜色作为补光。此外，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>&nbsp;也可以拍摄<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/4K\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">4K</a>分辨率视频及支持<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Live%20Photos\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Live Photos</a>。</div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Live%20Photos\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Live Photos</a>:一张活的照片，更确切的说，它是一段长度为 3 秒、还包括声音的小视频。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[3]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[3]_19921660\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\">更高的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">分辨率</a>意味着要处理更多的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%83%8F%E7%B4%A0\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">像素</a>。这也是为什么<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>&nbsp;的 A9 芯片（单核2394，多核4083）性能仍可击败新&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Android/60243\" data-lemmaid=\"60243\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Android</a>旗舰手机的原因之一，毕竟<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%88%86%E8%BE%A8%E7%8E%87\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">分辨率</a>更低总像素更少。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[6]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[6]_19921660\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"4_5\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub19921660_4_5\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"续航\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; text-indent: 0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">续航</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>&nbsp;4英寸屏幕相对来说能保证更持久的续航时间。在相同压力循环测试下，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>续航达到10个小时，比<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%206S\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 6S</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%205S\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 5S</a>续航多了两小时左右，比<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F/244153\" data-lemmaid=\"244153\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">三星</a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Galaxy%20S7\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Galaxy S7</a>更是多出近3个小时。</div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"4_6\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub19921660_4_6\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"网络\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; text-indent: 0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">网络</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>的两个型号A1724和A1723已经通过了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/3C%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">3C认证</a>和拿到了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%A5%E7%BD%91%E8%AE%B8%E5%8F%AF%E8%AF%81\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">入网许可证</a>。其中，前者支持<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8F%8C4G\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">双4G</a>网络，而后者则具备全网通功能，通吃移动，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%81%94%E9%80%9A\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">联通</a>和<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%94%B5%E4%BF%A1/15421798\" data-lemmaid=\"15421798\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">电信</a>的2G/3G/4G网络。除此之外，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>还有一个型号为A1662，在网络方面将支持移动2G和<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%81%94%E9%80%9A\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">联通</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%94%B5%E4%BF%A1/15421798\" data-lemmaid=\"15421798\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">电信</a>的2G/3G/4G网络。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[4]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[4]_19921660\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">4G+</span></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>的蜂窝网络与<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%206s\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 6s</a>（4G LTE Advanced）并不同，只支持<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/4G%20LTE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">4G LTE</a>，这一细微的差别意味着<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>将无法使用在中国市场正在快速建设的“<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/4G%2B\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">4G+</a>”网络。理论上，4G LTE下行速率为150Mbps，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/4G%20LTE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">4G LTE</a>&nbsp;Advanced则可达到300Mbps。技术上，区别在于<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%BD%BD%E6%B3%A2%E8%81%9A%E5%90%88\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">载波聚合</a>。<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%BD%BD%E6%B3%A2\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">载波</a>就好比无线通信中传输信息的“车道”，1个载波相当于1条车道，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%BD%BD%E6%B3%A2%E8%81%9A%E5%90%88\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">载波聚合</a>就是聚合两个以上<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%BD%BD%E6%B3%A2%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">载波传输</a>信息“车道”，单位时间内信息传输量提升到两倍以上，用户<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">下载</a>的速度就会更快、体验也更加流畅。尤其是在人群密集的区域，“4G+”网络的快速流畅更为明显。按照三大运营商的部署，下一步重点是在高校、商业区、交通枢纽等业务热点区域开通<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%BD%BD%E6%B3%A2%E8%81%9A%E5%90%88\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">载波聚合</a>功能。因此，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>在中国市场销售时将面临无法支持“4G+”网络的难题。<span style=\"font-size: 10.5px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[7]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[7]_19921660\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\">&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"anchor-list\" style=\"position: relative; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px;\"><a name=\"4_7\" class=\"lemma-anchor para-title\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"sub19921660_4_7\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a><a name=\"指纹识别\" class=\"lemma-anchor \" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: absolute; top: -50px;\"></a></div><div class=\"para-title level-3\" label-module=\"para-title\" style=\"clear: both; zoom: 1; margin: 20px 0px 12px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Verdana; text-indent: 0px;\"><h3 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400;\">指纹识别</h3></div><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>同<div class=\"lemma-picture text-pic layout-right\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 0px 3px; position: relative; float: right; clear: right; width: 220px;\"><a class=\"image-link\" nslog-type=\"9317\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/pic/iPhone%20SE/19420249/0/0b7b02087bf40ad1a5e3a6495e2c11dfa9ecce11?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"指纹识别\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none; display: block; width: 220px; height: 126px;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=8cc1af77a264034f0bcdc5049fc27980/0b7b02087bf40ad1a5e3a6495e2c11dfa9ecce11.jpg\" alt=\"指纹识别\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block; margin: 0px auto; width: 220px; height: 126px;\"></a><span class=\"description\" style=\"display: block; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 12px; text-indent: 0px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; line-height: 15px; padding: 8px 7px; min-height: 12px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224);\">指纹识别</span></div>样配备了<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Touch%20ID\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Touch ID</a>指纹识别功能，但是与<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%206s\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 6s</a>不同，并非是最新的一代。而<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%20SE\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone SE</a>则与<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%205s\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 5s</a>和<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%206\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 6</a>一样配备的是第一代<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Touch%20ID\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">Touch ID</a>模块，因此在识别速度上明显不如<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/iPhone%206s\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration: none;\">iPhone 6s</a>。<span style=\"font-size: